  "title": "Marketing Exec (TRAVELLING OPPORTUNITIES!!)",
  "description": "<p>“If you want to go fast, go alone. If you want to go far, go together” 🏃🏻‍♂️💨</p><p><br /></p><p>Royal Organisation is built on an energetic and driven work culture! </p><p><br /></p><p>We strongly value individual’s strengths! We believe that as a TEAM, we will always have new breakthroughs in the industry & we are looking for ideal candidates to further elevate the business!</p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p>✨ What We Do: ✨</p><p>• Grow our clients’ portfolio & branding through face to face marketing </p><p>• Increase sales revenues for clients </p><p>• Ensure professionalism in providing services to potential customers</p><p>• Manage roadshows & events </p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p>✨ What You Can Look Forward To: ✨</p><p>• Develop leadership skill</p><p>• Leading & coaching team to meet business objectives </p><p>• Overseas travelling exposure</p><p>•  Handling of campaign strategies </p><p>•  Team bonding activities </p><p>•  Experience to work with clients from wide range of industries</p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p>✨ Who Are We Looking For: ✨</p><p>•  Strong learning attitude </p><p>•  Good interpersonal skills </p><p>•  Solution driven</p><p>•  Highly driven to achieve personal & team targets</p><p>• Enjoys team-oriented environment </p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p>Keen to find out more? </p><p><br /></p><p>📍 Contact Minjie @ 97363434 now!</p>",
